name: The Outrage
description:
Outrage culture is addictive. My ego attach to hate, it allows me to feel superior, smarter, more aware, but also inability to feel connected to others. I exist in survival mode. It leads me to brain fog, fatigue, depression, insomnia.
To heal, I must CREATE, find joy, serve others, and become conscious to what I consume.

3000 x 2200 px
